Text::Template::Simple
======================

Simple text template engine.

Read the module's POD for documentation and examples.

INSTALLATION

Just use the cpan shell to install this module. From a command prompt, type:

    cpan

or

    perl -MCPAN -e shell

to enter the cpan shell. And then enter:

   install Text::Template::Simple

If you don't have the cpan shell available, then you have a broken perl
installation.

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules:

   Data::Dumper 2.101
   File::Spec   0.6
   File::Find   0.0
   IO::Handle   1.1505
   IO::File     1.06021
   Fcntl        1.03
   Safe         2.06
   Digest::MD5

these modules are only required for testing:

   Test::More   0.40
   File::Temp

and this module is recommended:

   Devel::Size  0.77

